\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My mom will always be my mom and to go even deeper\'85a woman will always be a woman!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But we live in a culture that is so driven and it is in a constant state to force all of us to proved ourselves.\
