\f0\b \cf3 \super 23\'a0
\f1\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub The man said,  \'93This is now bone of my bones\uc0\u8232 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0and flesh of my flesh;\u8232 she shall be called\'a0\'91woman,\'92\u8232 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0for she was taken out of man.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf3 \super 24\'a0
\f3\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub That is why a man leaves his father and mother and is united\'a0to his wife, and they become one flesh.      
\f1 \cf3 Gen 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In Gen 2 it makes this statement she has value because of who she is\'85not what she does or where she goes or what she provides or anything like that.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}She has inherent worth .\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}She is worth leaving everything behind and running toward.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf4 Tension:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But we live in a culture that wants to destroy that.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Advertising\'92s whole goal is to make you feel inadequate in every way so you buy their \'91solution\'92.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The internet has made the world small\'85which is great in some ways but terrible in others.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
