\f0\b \cf4 Transition:  Over time, when we aren\'92t even looking\'85what happens is we slowly start to lose our identity in who we are and start to place it in who we are with or not with.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 Who you marry or whether you have kids or not\'85\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our culture tells women this completely mixed up messed up message.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t need a man\'85but everything you watch on tv is all about love and finding the right person.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
